=====================================================================

Flatpak is new package management system built for simple, universal,
single-click  installations.  Games that "just work",  neatly stuffed
and safely locked in sandbox.


System Requirements:

OS: x86_64 Linux
Memory: 4GB
CPU: Intel Core i3
Graphics Card: Strongly recommended
Disk Space: 2.6GB in home folder
Flatpak support: Check http://flatpak.org/getting.html for more info
Graphics: OpenGL 3.0 or better, tested with Intel and NVidia Official drivers
